(Musik)

00:04:58.260 --> 00:04:59.260
(Tepuk tangan)

00:04:59.260 --> 00:05:01.260
Terima kasih.

00:05:01.260 --> 00:05:05.260
(Tepuk tangan)

00:05:05.260 --> 00:05:07.260
Terima kasih.

